   <talk_paragraph index="n133_lena_duglars-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Lady Lena${action:Talk}<BR>We meet so often in the castle.<BR>If you need a job, why don't you go outside the castle?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n280_saint_guard-1-a" mid="21" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Explains the situation)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Malcolm$<BR>Who, who are you!<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Scared guard shouts)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n280_saint_guard-1-b" mid="25" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What? A lady?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Malcolm$<BR>Oh, okay. Joey sent you.<BR>Oh, no... So, my <FONT color=#a82424>lady</FONT> must not be coming....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n280_saint_guard-1-c" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Who were you going to meet?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Malcolm$<BR>Umm... I was going to meet somebody here today.<BR>
I'm going to wait until she comes. I... I will never leave!!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n280_saint_guard-1-d" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Malcolm shouts excitedly)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Malcolm$<BR>My fair <FONT color=#a82424>noble</FONT> lady!<BR>I told her how I felt about her and gave her a very expensive <FONT color=#a82424>necklace</FONT> as a present. I was so nervous.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n280_saint_guard-1-e" mid="32" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>If you don't go back soon, you'll be prosecuted as a deserter.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Malcolm$<BR>I asked her if she accepts my feelings, wear that <FONT color=#a82424>necklace</FONT> and come out here.<BR>
If she declines... I asked her to decline my feelings here. So, I'll keep on waiting!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n280_saint_guard-1-f" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Malcolm starts thinking)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Malcolm$<BR>I... am... not... afraid... of that. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(It is indeed scary becoming a deserter)</FONT> What should I do? I can't leave until she comes.... I used my monthly salary to buy that necklace....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n280_saint_guard-1-g" mid="36" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What should I tell her?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Malcolm$<BR>Umm... I have a request.<BR>
I'll be waiting here a little longer, so could you go to the <FONT color=#a82424>lady</FONT> and give her a message?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n280_saint_guard-1-h" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay. Who's that lady?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Malcolm$<BR>Accept my feelings.... Or... umm, <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Malcolm hesitates)</FONT> Umm, get my necklace back... That's kind of expensive... <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Can't hear him very well since he's mumbling)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-1-h" image="QN_Npc_Lena_Duglars.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n280_saint_guard-1-i" mid="65" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>So are you going to continue to wait here?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Malcolm$<BR>She comes to the Saint Haven <FONT color=#a82424>Castle</FONT> very often. Her name is <FONT color=#a82424>Lady Lena</FONT>.... I fell in love at the first sight of her fire-red hair and pure white dress. Haha, well, thank you!!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-1-i" image="QN_Npc_Lena_Duglars.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="66"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Malcolm$<BR>I have no choice… My next duty is at <FONT color=#a82424>Dark Overlord Training Camp</FONT>. <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, please go and convey the message that I'll be waiting there.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n280_saint_guard-2" image="QN_Npc_Lena_Duglars.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Malcolm$<BR>Please go to the Saint Haven Castle and pass on my message to <FONT color=#a82424>Lady Lena</FONT>. If she declines my feelings, I would at least like my necklace back.... I'm not moving until you come back.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n252_saint_guard-2" image="QN_Npc_Elite_Soilder.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Joey$<BR>Did you meet <FONT color=#a82424>Malcolm</FONT>?<BR>If he doesn't come back soon, he really will become a deserter.... I'm so worried.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n133_lena_duglars-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n133_lena_duglars-2-a" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Explains the situation)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Lady Lena${action:Talk}<BR>What is it? If you need someone to play with, find someone else.<BR>I have a lot to think about, so I'm not able to play with you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n133_lena_duglars-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n133_lena_duglars-2-b" mid="47" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Lena takes out a necklace)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Lady Lena$<BR>What? What love confession?<BR>...Oh, then this necklace is....<FONT color=#7e12d2> (Lena searches her pocket)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n133_lena_duglars-2-b" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300255" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n133_lena_duglars-2-c" mid="49" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You... didn't know.... (What a pity)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$Lady Lena$<BR>One day, I went to see a military parade and some soldier gave me this necklace and ran away. I think he said something... but I couldn't hear what he was saying, so I just forgot about him.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n133_lena_duglars-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n133_lena_duglars-2-d" mid="51" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>He at least wants his necklace back...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>$Lady Lena${action:Talk}<BR>He didn't even explain himself clearly, and just ran away.<BR>These day, I have much worries to take care of, so I can't take care of these small things.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n133_lena_duglars-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n133_lena_duglars-2-e" mid="53" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Alright.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="52"><![CDATA[<html>$Lady Lena$<BR>Is there a reason for me to go in person?<BR>Since you came to pass on his words, could you, <FONT color=#a82424>instead</FONT> of me, return to him and give him the necklace?</html>]]></talk_question>
